    <section aria-labelledby="access-heading">
      <h2 id="access-heading">Why We Need Access to Your Google Account</h2>
      <p>We require access to your Google account to upload videos to your YouTube channel. The OAuth scopes requested are:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>youtube.upload</strong> – Upload videos to YouTube</li>
        <li><strong>gmail.send</strong> (if used) – Send alerts and confirmations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Your data is secure, and you can revoke access at any time via Google’s account settings.</p>
    </section>

